snippet.title: A.I.L.A – Official Trailer (EN) | Gamescom Europe 2024
snippet.description:
Wishlist A.I.L.A on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2695430/AILA/

A.I.L.A is a first-person psychological horror game where you play as a game tester for a new, state-of-the-art videogame AI. Survive terrifying worlds within worlds as the line between the real and the virtual becomes unclear...

Coming in 2025.
Follow A.I.L.A on X: https://x.com/PlayAILA
Join the A.I.L.A Discord: https://discord.gg/RZQScNmWBU
